                    <Class>
                        <__p_name>ParseController</__p_name>
                        <__p_description>This is the singleton parse controller class. This controls the execution of a given abstract parser. A slot is provided for starting a new parser. Signals are provided for status changes of this controller. This singleton class is in its own thread to not block the main GUI thread when a parser is executing.</__p_description>
