                        <Class>
                            <__p_name>PlainTextEdit</__p_name>
                            <__p_description>This is the plain text class. It provides additional functionality to its inherited class. Misspelled words are highlighted. A shortcut is provided to open a larger text editor dialog that has additional spell checking functionality. Misspelled word highlighting and the editor dialog popup features can be enabled or disabled.</__p_description>
