                        <Class>
                            <__p_name>InsertCommand</__p_name>
                            <__p_description>This is the insert command class. It implements the abstract command class.  It inherits from the remove command class because the insert command is simply the inverse of the remove command and therefore only needs to reverse the undo and redo commands.</__p_description>
